-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-bac-nam-gia-canh-tranh-dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien_mien_bac-dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-mien-nam.html\/#2_Tu_van_ho_tro-_cham_soc_khach_hang_chu_dao_nhiet_tinh\" title=\"2. T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3- ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng chu \u0111\u00e1o, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh\">2. T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3- ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng chu \u0111\u00e1o, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-bac-nam-gia-canh-tranh-dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien_mien_bac-dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-mien-nam.html\/#3_Quan_tam_va_de_tam_den_tung_chi_tiet\" title=\"3. Quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft\">3. Quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-bac-nam-gia-canh-tranh-dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien_mien_bac-dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-mien-nam.html\/#_4_Trang_thiet_bi_hien_dai\" title=\"\u00a04. Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i\">\u00a04. Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-bac-nam-gia-canh-tranh-dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien_mien_bac-dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-mien-nam.html\/#5_Gia_ca_hop_ly\" title=\"5. Gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd\">5. Gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-1'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-bac-nam-gia-canh-tranh-dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien_mien_bac-dich-vu-chup-anh-su-kien-mien-nam.html\/#Cam_ket_dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien_cua_A_Chau_Media\" title=\"Cam k\u1ebft d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\u00a0\">Cam k\u1ebft d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em>Ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n l\u00e0 ghi l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh m\u00e0 qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n,\u00a0 C\u00f4ng ty t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n <strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong> s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch; ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, lu\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i mi\u1ec1n b\u1eafc v\u00e0 nam.<\/em><\/p>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"De_co_nhung_buc_anh_su_kien_sang_tao_can_phai_lam_gi\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Xac_dinh_loai_su_kien_minh_sap_chup\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">1. X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh s\u1eafp ch\u1ee5p<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n th\u00ec h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o, liveshow, team building, ti\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi h\u1ecfi, sinh nh\u1eadt,\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1ecdi chung l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t th\u00ec m\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee5p c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 khai th\u00e1c ri\u00eang. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o th\u00ec c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i bi\u1ec3u, nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng xoay quanh; c\u00f2n ti\u1ec7c c\u01b0\u1edbi th\u00ec c\u00f4 d\u00e2u ch\u00fa r\u1ec3 l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh n\u00ean c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u trong \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh,\u2026 Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef9 lo\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee5p l\u00e0 g\u00ec.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15152\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15152\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15152 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/teemu-paananen-bzdhc5b3Bxs-unsplash-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Chup-anh-su-kien\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1829\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/teemu-paananen-bzdhc5b3Bxs-unsplash-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/teemu-paananen-bzdhc5b3Bxs-unsplash-300x214.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/teemu-paananen-bzdhc5b3Bxs-unsplash-1024x731.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/teemu-paananen-bzdhc5b3Bxs-unsplash-768x549.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/teemu-paananen-bzdhc5b3Bxs-unsplash-1536x1097.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/teemu-paananen-bzdhc5b3Bxs-unsplash-2048x1463.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15152\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh xem ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Xac_dinh_chu_de_noi_dung_cua_su_kien_sap_chup\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">2. X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1, n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n s\u1eafp ch\u1ee5p<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh xong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 n\u00ean th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1eafm r\u00f5 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n l\u00e0 g\u00ec, n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3n \u1ea3nh, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh n\u00e0o c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m r\u00f5&#8230;. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1ea5n m\u00e1y ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean tham quan v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n s\u1eafp di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ch\u1ee5p v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.\u200b<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15153\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15153\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15153 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/chuttersnap-Q_KdjKxntH8-unsplash-1-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"Chup-anh-su-kien\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1709\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/chuttersnap-Q_KdjKxntH8-unsplash-1-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/chuttersnap-Q_KdjKxntH8-unsplash-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/chuttersnap-Q_KdjKxntH8-unsplash-1-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/chuttersnap-Q_KdjKxntH8-unsplash-1-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/chuttersnap-Q_KdjKxntH8-unsplash-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/chuttersnap-Q_KdjKxntH8-unsplash-1-2048x1367.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15153\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1, n\u1ed9i dung c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n s\u1eafp ch\u1ee5p<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Canh_goc_chup_va_lay_anh_sang_phu_hop\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">3. Canh g\u00f3c ch\u1ee5p v\u00e0 l\u1ea5y \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\u1ede nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1n ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, g\u00f3c ch\u1ee5p\u2026 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 trong studio. Khi ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean t\u1eeb c\u00e1c khung c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0o hay \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ch\u00f9m \u0111\u00e8n neon, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap cho b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0.<\/li>\n<li>H\u00e3y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00f3c ch\u1ee5p th\u00f4ng minh. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a ch\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb g\u00f3c ch\u00e9o, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ee9ng, ng\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o k\u00edch th\u00edch ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem. N\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 zoom ho\u1eb7c l\u1ea5y ti\u00eau c\u1ef1 xa. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 1 ch\u00fat kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng set h\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Lua_chon_nhung_trang_thiet_bi_chup_anh_chuyen_dung_phu_hop_voi_su_kien\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">4. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea5t k\u00ec h\u00e3ng m\u00e1y \u1ea3nh n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00ec h\u00e3y ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nhanh c\u1ee7a thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, cho d\u00f9 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra trong nh\u00e0 hay ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec c\u00e1c \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh nh\u01b0 Lens fix, \u1ed0ng g\u00f3c r\u1ed9ng, \u1ed0ng g\u00f3c trung, \u1ed0ng Tele, Lens zoom, flash\u2026 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 cho m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee3 ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15154\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15154\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15154 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/9.jpg\" alt=\"chup-anh-su-kien\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/9.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/9-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/9-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15154\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_diem_cong_tot_nhat_ma_chup_anh_su_kien_A_Chau_Media_mang_den_quy_khach\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>5 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media mang \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch ch\u00ednh c\u1eeda qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch\u00a0l\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cho\u00a0c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty, doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ty, sinh nh\u1eadt c\u00f4ng ty, ra m\u1eaft s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o, h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb\u2026\u00a0hay l\u01b0u gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 trong c\u01b0\u1edbi h\u1ecfi, sinh nh\u1eadt&#8230;. C\u00e1c nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ch\u1ee5p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, ch\u00e2n th\u1ef1c. M\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u00e8m theo ch\u1ec9 di\u1ec5n ra m\u1ed9t\u00a0l\u1ea7n duy nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u mang nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau. Cho n\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 ghi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u00fd ngh\u0129a \u1ea5y, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ekip \u201cc\u00f3 t\u00e2m\u201d.<\/li>\n<li>N\u1ebfu qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t, h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay <strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong> &#8211; \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Nhung_buc_biet_ke_chuyen_qua_tung_hinh_anh\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">1. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c bi\u1ebft k\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec7n qua t\u1eebng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh:<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2m &#8220;Tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc&#8221;, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n cho d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng &#8220;nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh bi\u1ebft k\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec7n&#8221;. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n,<strong> \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong> hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb c\u1ea5p cao, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf hay ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n,\u2026 \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c con ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Qua nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u01b0\u1ee3c ghi l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u, ai \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfu tham d\u1ef1 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15155\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15155\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15155 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/10.jpg\" alt=\"Chup- anh-su-kien\" width=\"1000\" height=\"603\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/10.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/10-300x181.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/10-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15155\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c bi\u1ebft k\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec7n qua t\u1eebng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Tu_van_ho_tro-_cham_soc_khach_hang_chu_dao_nhiet_tinh\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">2. T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3- ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng chu \u0111\u00e1o, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><b>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media <\/b>lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n l\u00f2ng l\u1eafng nghe \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c ho\u00e1 th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch.\u00a0Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh tinh t\u1ebf, t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa, lan to\u1ea3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 cho c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang bi\u1ebft qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0 ai, l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb m\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n\u00a0\u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn.<\/li>\n<li>Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc m\u00e0 qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n ghi l\u1ea1i;\u00a0Chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp li\u00ean l\u1ea1c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>Sau khi ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng tin y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch qua ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ebfp \u1ea3nh gia ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Quan_tam_va_de_tam_den_tung_chi_tiet\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">3. Quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc<\/li>\n<li>T\u1eadn t\u00e2m l\u00e0m n\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/li>\n<li>X\u1eed l\u00fd h\u1eadu k\u00ec- cung c\u1ea5p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15156\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15156\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15156 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/11.jpg\" alt=\"Chup-anh-su-kien\" width=\"1000\" height=\"664\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/11.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/11-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/11-768x510.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15156\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_4_Trang_thiet_bi_hien_dai\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">\u00a04. Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t set h\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0o m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 k\u0129 thu\u1eadt, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb nh\u01b0 flycam, gimbal , c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i boom m\u00e1y quay hay micro,\u2026 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u1ea5t, r\u00f5 n\u00e9t nh\u1ea5t. Trong c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng gian trong nh\u00e0, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1edd \u1ea3o c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i v\u0169 h\u1ed9i hay d\u1ea1 ti\u1ec7c, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 flash c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1eabn b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t k\u00ec kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_15157\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-15157\" style=\"width: 1000px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-15157 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/12.jpg\" alt=\"Chup-anh-su-kien\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/12.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/12-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/12-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-15157\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Trang thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Gia_ca_hop_ly\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ed1c24;\">5. Gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c chi ph\u00ed h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t. V\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tri k\u1ec9, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i, nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 l\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.\u00a0N\u1ebfu qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f2n \u0111ang ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n trong vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, event, h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb h\u00e3y t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u1eefng set h\u00ecnh ch\u00e2n th\u1ef1c, sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng, ghi l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd thu h\u00fat qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ngay t\u1eeb \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<\/li>\n<li><em>B\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tham kh\u1ea3o:\u00a0<\/em><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14427 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1030\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien.png 1030w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien-300x105.png 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien-1024x360.png 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien-768x270.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1030px) 100vw, 1030px\" \/><\/p>\n<h1><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cam_ket_dich_vu_chup_anh_su_kien_cua_A_Chau_Media\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Cam k\u1ebft d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h1>\n<p><strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong>\u00a0d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3, cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u sau \u0111\u00e2y:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>CH\u1ea4T L\u01af\u1ee2NG<\/strong>\u00a0v\u00e0 s\u1ef1\u00a0<strong>UY T\u00cdN<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00e0m n\u00ean<strong> Th\u01b0\u01a1ng Hi\u1ec7u \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media <\/strong>v\u00ec th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169<strong> \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media <\/strong>lu\u00f4n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t trong<strong>\u00a0quy tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n:\u00a0<\/strong>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb\u00a0<\/strong>c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1edbm\u00a0<\/strong>h\u01a1n v\u1edbi<strong>\u00a0th\u1eddi gian quy \u0111\u1ecbnh\u00a0<\/strong>khi ch\u1ea1y ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh<strong>.<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Lu\u00f4n\u00a0<strong>\u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\u00a0<\/strong>c\u1ee7a<strong>\u00a0ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>\u00dd T\u01af\u1edeNG S\u00c1NG T\u1ea0O\u00a0<\/strong>c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c trong m\u1ed7i ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m m\u1edbi m\u00ecnh c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh sau.<strong>\u00a0\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong> lu\u00f4n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 c\u00e1c y\u00eau t\u1ed1 sau :\n<ul>\n<li><strong>S\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>S\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Lu\u00f4n b\u00e1m s\u00e1t v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>NHI\u1ec6T HUY\u1ebeT N\u0102NG \u0110\u1ed8NG\u00a0<\/strong>v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ebb lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng g\u1ee1 r\u1ed1i trong c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t. V\u00ec th\u1ebf quy tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, <strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong> lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 :\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1<\/strong>\u00a0tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ee9ng ra qu\u1ea3n l\u00ed c\u00e1c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n.<\/li>\n<li><strong>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3\u00a0<\/strong>h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh khi c\u00f3 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng hay x\u1ea3y ra.<\/li>\n<li><strong>S\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng\u00a0<\/strong>ti\u1ebfp \u1ee9ng khi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li><strong>CHI PH\u00cd TI\u1ebeT KI\u1ec6M\u00a0<\/strong>so v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a kh\u